    public class VoidViewState<V extends MvpLceView<java.lang.Void>>
extends AbsParcelableLceViewState<java.lang.Void,V>
    If you really have good reasons you could have Void as content type in a LCE (Loading-Content-Error) View. This is the corresponding LceViewState andRestoreableViewState

    Can be used for Activites and Fragments.
